{"tid":1046901,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG 漏斗胸討論區","createTime":"2019-03-04T14:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T18:00:20.000Z","uid":231730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"932500ac23e329c3d0e4bd70f44c8fc2700340b2","tid":1046901,"uid":231730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟我個妹就有漏斗胸嘅問題<br />\n細個因為屋企人見佢又無乜健康問題<br />\n老豆話 既然無事 何必要無啦啦捱一刀<br />\n所以到佢今年22歲 U都就畢業<br />\n都未曾做過手術<br />\n咁我作為佢大佬都出左黎工作左1年<br />\n儲左10萬俾佢 等佢做手術<br />\n<br />\n想係度問問各位巴打<br />\n究竟公立同私院 有無大分別<br />\n有無巴絲係私立醫院睇過<br />\n我傾向想佢做微創 好似會快d 好返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手上路，大家分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ceca1b846d8ab46f9dc50443d936b267461dda9","tid":1046901,"uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲，呼吸有冇困難？有冇壓到其它器官"},{"pid":"ba91b6b31565d369152735d9bb5db6defb119b10","tid":1046901,"uid":154655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d5f03dafe7eb1e22ef279add1f1467a464749e","tid":1046901,"uid":231730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ceca1b846d8ab46f9dc50443d936b267461dda9","tid":1046901,"uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲，呼吸有冇困難？有冇壓到其它器官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"22歲<br />\n佢一跑步就 呼吸困難<br />\n器官無乜點壓"},{"pid":"a6fea13e8f46877587c3e56aa0c4f1d8a71d48dc","tid":1046901,"uid":231730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba91b6b31565d369152735d9bb5db6defb119b10","tid":1046901,"uid":154655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:41:42.000Z","msg"